title: ECHO Game Soundtrack (2017)
description: All music for the game ECHO, ripped (not recorded) from the uncompressed game content itself, cleaned up, and encoded with LAME vbr -V0. Until an official soundtrack is released, this is the best available unofficial soundtrack (at the time of posting). If you like this music, please support the game developer by purchasing the game. http://www.echo-game.com Track list: 01.Opening 02.Arrival 03.The Surface 04.Infinity 05.The First Blackout 06.She's Waking Up 07.Light 08.Evolution 09.New Gods 10.The Voice of Eternity 11.A New Challenge 12.Purity 13.Learning 14.Shutdown -r -f 15.Restart 16.Awaken 17.Outside 18.A Dark Challenge 19.Oblivion 20.Reawaken 21.Enlightenment 22.Bridge of Light 23.Memory 24.Final Restart 25.The Last Door 26.End Credits 27.ECHO
